                    <h4>Temazcal</h4>
                    <p>With us to guide the ritual will be an expert Chaman with more than ten years of experience in Mexico, and some special occasions will be guided by the grandmother, grandma (It's traditionally called "abuelita" because these women have been doing this ritual since more than 30 years. Hey: do not think that taking Temazcal with a grandmother will be softer, in fact, it is the opposite, the ceremonies with the grandmothers are the ones where the body and the spirit are worked the most.</p>
                    <p>The Temazcal is a ceremony that must be respected for how much it represented and represents for the culture and for the people who still practice it. You must know that the Temazcal reaches high temperatures, so at any time you may go out if you need it, we only ask for total respect. Enjoy, the experience is strong but bearable and helps to purify, connect, and know more about the Mexican Cosmovision.</p>
